---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import APAReferenceGenerator from '../../components/APAReferenceGenerator';
import SimilarTools from '../../components/SimilarTools';
---

<Layout title="AI APA Reference Generator - AI-Free-Forever">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-emerald-100/50 py-16 mb-12 rounded-2xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        AI APA Reference Generator
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Generate accurate APA style references for any source. Create properly formatted citations with ease.
      </p>
    </div>
    <APAReferenceGenerator client:load />
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Create Perfect Citations Instantly with Our AI APA Reference Generator – 100% Free</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">Struggling to format citations in APA style correctly? Our AI APA Reference Generator takes the guesswork out of academic referencing, allowing you to create flawless APA citations in seconds — all tailored to the latest APA guidelines.</p>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Powered by advanced GPT-4o technology, the AI APA Reference Generator is completely free to use — no hidden fees, no subscription plans, no word limits. Whether you're writing a research paper, thesis, dissertation, or academic article, this tool ensures your references are accurate, professional, and ready to submit.</p>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Each citation is:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li class="text-lg">Correctly formatted according to the latest APA style (7th edition)</li>
          <li class="text-lg">Instantly generated based on your input</li>
          <li class="text-lg">Ready for immediate use in your bibliography or reference list</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">No more citation errors, manual formatting headaches, or wasted time — just fast, precise references you can trust.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">How to Generate APA References in 4 Easy Steps</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Using the AI APA Reference Generator is simple, fast, and stress-free:</p>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Choose Your Source Type</span>
            <p>Select the type of material you're citing — book, journal article, website, report, or more.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Enter Source Details</span>
            <p>Provide basic details like author names, publication dates, titles, URLs, DOIs, and publisher information.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Generate Your APA Citation</span>
            <p>Click "Generate," and our AI will instantly format your source into a perfect APA citation.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Copy and Paste</span>
            <p>Review the citation, make any optional edits, then copy it directly into your paper or bibliography.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Why Students and Researchers Rely on the AI APA Reference Generator</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">100% APA Style Compliance</h3>
            <p>The AI APA Reference Generator is updated with the latest APA 7th edition standards to ensure every citation is correct.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Saves Time and Reduces Stress</h3>
            <p>No more flipping through style guides or second-guessing punctuation, italics, and formatting details.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Supports All Common Source Types</h3>
            <p>From scholarly articles to blog posts and government reports, our AI can generate citations for a wide variety of materials.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Unlimited Free Usage</h3>
            <p>Create as many references as you need without worrying about daily limits, subscriptions, or hidden costs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Who Benefits Most From the AI APA Reference Generator?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Our AI APA Reference Generator is perfect for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">College Students:</span> Create flawless citations for essays, research projects, and coursework.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Graduate Students:</span> Build accurate reference lists for theses, dissertations, and academic journals.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Researchers and Scholars:</span> Save hours on citation formatting while ensuring academic credibility.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Teachers and Professors:</span> Quickly create citation examples for assignments, syllabi, and resource lists.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Writers and Journalists:</span> Properly attribute sources when writing nonfiction, articles, or whitepapers.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Tips for Getting the Best Results from the AI APA Reference Generator</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Maximize Your Accuracy:</p>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Tip</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Why It Matters</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Input Complete Details</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">For the best citation, make sure to include as much source information as possible — especially DOIs or URLs for digital materials.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Select the Correct Source Type</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">APA rules vary slightly between books, journal articles, websites, and reports. Choosing the right category ensures perfect formatting.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Double-Check Special Cases</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">APA has specific rules for missing authors, undated sources, or unusual publication types. The AI handles these, but reviewing unusual citations is always wise.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Use Proper Capitalization</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">APA style requires sentence case for titles — only the first word and proper nouns are capitalized.</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions About the AI APA Reference Generator</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is the AI APA Reference Generator really free to use?</h3>
            <p>Yes, it's 100% free with no subscriptions, payment walls, or usage limits.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Which APA edition does the tool follow?</h3>
            <p>It generates citations according to the APA 7th Edition guidelines — the latest version required by most universities.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What types of sources can I cite?</h3>
            <p>Books, journal articles, websites, reports, YouTube videos, podcasts, blogs, conference papers, government documents, and more.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How fast do I get the citation?</h3>
            <p>Instantly! Just enter the source details and click generate.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do I need to create an account?</h3>
            <p>No account required — just open the tool, input your source, and get your citation.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is my information stored or saved?</h3>
            <p>No. For your privacy, we do not save any citation data after your session ends.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">AI APA Reference Generator vs. Manual Formatting and Paid Tools</h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Feature</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">aiFreeForever AI APA Reference Generator</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Paid Citation Tools</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Manual Formatting</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Price</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Always Free</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">$10–$30 monthly</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Free</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Turnaround Time</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Instant</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Seconds to minutes</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Hours</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Supports Multiple Source Types</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Yes</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Depends on service</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Manual effort</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">APA 7th Edition Compliance</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Always</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Varies</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Risk of errors</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Account Required</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">No</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Usually</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">No</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Start Citing Smarter Today</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Use the AI APA Reference Generator now to create flawless, professional APA citations in seconds — saving you time, improving your academic writing, and ensuring you meet the highest standards, all for free.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-emerald-50 p-6 rounded-xl text-center mb-8">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold">👉 Start using the AI APA Reference Generator today and never worry about citation formatting again!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <SimilarTools currentToolPath="apa-reference" category="student" client:load />
  </main>
</Layout>